<p>配备超大轮毂与独特的猫眼绿配色，散发出浓烈运动与个性气息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200806/9e6330e1a2c946c3a4dc4f472d8ec2ed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
